OMB Number: 

15450166.



Form Number: 

IRS Form 4255.



Type of Review: 

Extension.



Title: 

Recapture of Investment Credit.



Description: 

Internal Revenue Code (IRC) 50(a) and Regs. section 1.47 require that taxpayers attach a statement to their return
showing the computation of the recapture tax when investment credit property is disposed of before the end of the recapture
period used in the original computation of the investment credit. 


